(133, 1, '2010-03-02 23:33:28', '2010-03-02 23:33:28', '<p><img class=" alignleft size-full wp-image-132" src="http://somaticexperiencing.com/export/wp-content/uploads/2010/03/reversing-chronic-pain-c.jpg" border="0" alt="Reversing Chronic Pain Cover" align="left" width="180" height="270" /></p> <h6><em>Foreword by Peter Levine</em></h6> <p><a href="http://www.amazon.com/Reversing-Chronic-Pain-10-Point-All-Natural/dp/1556436769/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;s=books&amp;qid=1267573120&amp;sr=1-1" target="_blank" title="Purchase Through Amazon"><br />Purchase through Amazon</a></p> <p> </p> <p> </p>  <!--more-->  <p> </p> <h5>From Amazon.com</h5> <p><br />Reversing Chronic Pain offers a dynamic framework for joining body and mind to speed the healing of traumatic pain from the body level up. Each chapter presents a body-centered skill set that can be mastered through a broad menu of practice exercises. The resulting interlinked somatic building blocks help readers shift from physical pain to body awareness, and from unstoppable suffering to heartfelt connection and peace.<br /><br /></p>', 'Reversing Chronic Pain by Maggie Phillips', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'reversing-chronic-pain-by-maggie-phillips', '', '', '2010-03-02 23:33:28', '2010-03-02 23:33:28', '', 0, 'http://somaticexperiencing.com/export/2010/03/02/reversing-chronic-pain-by-maggie-phillips/', 11, 'post', '', 0),
