(195, 1, '2012-02-17 19:21:46', '2012-02-17 19:21:46', '<p>*Note: Read the following or download the pdf <a href="http://somaticexperiencing.com/stories/articles/Calliflower/Instructions_for_Joining_FHE_Conference_Call.pdf">here</a>.</p> <p><b>Instructions for Joining FHE Conference Call: </b></p> <p>We now have an FHE dedicated conference call line through Calliflower service. Anyone can join into a  conference call by phone or Skype at any time without having to schedule a call.  There is one shared pin  number to join the call.</p> <p><b>Shared Pin Number:<b style="outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; font-size: 16px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;">8467</b></b></p> <p> </p> <p><b>TO JOIN THE CALL BY PHONE:</b></p> <p>1. Call your  local dial in-­‐numbers from the list of International Dial-­‐In Numbers</p> <p>2. After the call connects dial Pin Number:<b> </b></p> <p>(Boulder/Denver Dial-‐in Number:303-‐330-‐0974)</p> <p> </p> <p><b><i>(Free. No Skype credit needed)</i></b></p> <p>1. Open Skype.</p> <p>2. Add calliflowerskypeas a Skype contact.</p> <p>3. At the scheduled time, call <b>calliflowerskype</b> from Skype</p> <p>4. Click the "dial pad" icon to see your dial pad.</p> <p>5. Dial Pin Number:<b style="outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; font-size: 16px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;">8467</b><b> </b></p> <p><b>&nbsp;</b> 6. You should now be connected to the call!</p> <p><b><br /></b></p> <p><i><br /></i></p> <p><b>TO JOIN THE CALL FROM SKYPE</b></p> <p><b>: </b></p> <p>1. Open Skype.</p> <p>2. Add 	 as a Skype contact.</p> <p>3. At the scheduled time, call <b>calliflowerskype</b> from Skype</p> <p>4. Click the "dial pad" icon to see your dial pad.</p> <p>5. Dial Pin Number:<strong>8467</strong><b>&nbsp;</b></p> <p><b>&nbsp;</b> 6. You should now be connected to the call!</p> <p> </p> <p><strong>International Dial In Numbers</strong></p> <tabl