(221, 1, '2013-03-06 08:00:00', '2013-03-06 08:00:00', '<p style="text-align: center;"><img class=" size-full wp-image-218" src="http://somaticexperiencing.com/export/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/SD_Case_Consult.jpg" width="671" height="303" alt="SD Case Consult" style="border: 2px solid #2b84c8; padding: 2px;" width="671" height="303" /></p> <p>The SE® Trauma Institute is privileged to offer a day of case consultations and supervision with author and founder of the Somatic Experiencing® trauma resolution model, Peter A. Levine, PhD.&nbsp;</p> <p>Open to Therapists using body focused approaches, body workers, chiropractors, acupuncturists, nurses, etc. and open to training participants and practitioners of Somatic Experiencing®. The Day is geared for Intermediate students or above, however, Beginners are welcome to present a case or ask questions. Each three hours of consultation time equals one hour credit toward the required eighteen hours for SEP certification. <strong>Remember to bring your session log to receive SEP credit.&nbsp;</strong></p> <blockquote> <p><em>"This is an ideal opportunity to observe Peter modeling his highly creative, intelligent and sensitve healing skills in an intimate and comfortable environment. His demonstrations and explantions furthered my understanding of the myriad of compleixties and simplicities of Somatic Experiencing®. This last supervision with Peter was unforgettable, profound, inspiring and a very encouraging experience for me as a practitioner." </em>Victoria Mihich, MA, MFT, SEP</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;<a href="index.php?option=com_eventbooking&amp;view=category&amp;Itemid=110" title="Event Page" target="_blank"><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><strong>You can register by clicking here.</strong></span></a></p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <ul> <li><a href="https://somaticexperiencing.com/events/consult-registration.html?task=view_event&amp;event_id=16" title="All Day Signup">All Day Registration</a>: (11am-6pm, worth 2 Consult Hours)<span style="font-size: 14pt;"><strong></strong></span></li> <li><a href="https://somaticexperiencing.com/events/consult-registration.html?task=view_event&amp;event_id=14" title="Afternoon Signup">Afternoon (2nd half) Registration</a>: (3pm-6pm, worth 1 Consult Hour)</li> <li><a href="https://somaticexperiencing.com/events/consult-registration.html?task=view_event&amp;event_id=15" title="Morning Sign Up">Morning (1st Half) Registration</a>:&nbsp;(11am-2pm, worth 1 Consult Hour)</li> </ul> <p><span style="line-height: 1.3em;">Please contact Joan Luly for </span><a href="http://localhost:8888/speed/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/caseconsultflyer1.pdf" target="_blank" style="line-height: 1.3em;">more information</a><span style="line-height: 1.3em;">: </span><a href="mailto:joansehealing@mac.com" style="line-height: 1.3em;">joansehealing@mac.com</a><span style="line-height: 1.3em;">.</span></p> <p><span style="line-height: 1.3em;"><a href="http://somaticexperiencing.com/export/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/may11.13reg_consult.pdf" title="Registration form and Check" target="_blank">Snail Mail Option</a>.&nbsp;</span></p> <p><a href="http://localhost:8888/speed/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/peter_case_consult_san_diego_may1120131.pdf" title="Event Flyer" target="_blank"><span style="line-height: 1.3em;">Also, the Flier</span></a></p> <p>If you are interested in having Peter see a client of yours, please contact Justin Snavely at <a href="mailto:traumahealing@gmail.com">traumahealing@gmail.com</a>&nbsp;with the following information:</p> <ol> <li>First name and age of client.</li> <li>Brief list of relevant trauma history (Including the age that it occurred)</li> <li>Ways in which therapy is stuck.</li> <li>Ways in which therapy is advancing.</li> <li>Why do you specifically want Peter to see this client.&nbsp;</li> </ol> <p>NOTE: NO cancellations can be made after May 8th, 2013. Thank you.&nbsp;</p> </blockquote>', 'Peter Levine Group Case Consultation in San Diego - May 11th!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'peter-levine-group-case-consultation-in-san-diego-may-11th', '', '', '2013-03-06 08:00:00', '2013-03-06 08:00:00', '', 0, 'http://somaticexperiencing.com/export/2013/03/06/peter-levine-group-case-consultation-in-san-diego-may-11th/', 2, 'post', '', 0),
