(223, 1, '2013-03-18 22:58:20', '2013-03-18 22:58:20', '<p><a target="_blank" title="Kids in the House website" href="http://kidsinthehouse.com"><img class=" size-full wp-image-222" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" alt="kidsinthehouse" src="http://localhost:8888/speed/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/kidsinthehouse1.jpg" height="250" width="521" width="521" height="250" /></a></p> <p>Dr. Levine has agreed to take part in a shoot this Thursday for <a target="_blank" title="Kids in the hosue home page" href="http://kidsinthehouse.com">Kidsinthehouse.com</a>, a online video resource for parents that is designed to offer searchable, quick results from professionals and fellow parents alike. We invite you to check out their site, (which is still under development) and sign up for future news. We have been given access to the early beta, and the footage is amazing. With the vast amount of content there, we are sure that this website will definitely be of immense help to parents everywhere. Peter''s co-author, Maggie Kline, will also be featured. Head on to their website and check out the Sizzle Reel.</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Kids in the House - Resources for Parents', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'kids-in-the-house-resources-for-parents', '', '', '2013-03-18 22:58:20', '2013-03-18 22:58:20', '', 0, 'http://somaticexperiencing.com/export/2013/03/18/kids-in-the-house-resources-for-parents/', 2, 'post', '', 0),
